# BeFirst AOI Service - API Refactoring Status

**Project**: ExtractorAOIs Windows Service → REST API Migration
**Date**: 2026-04-08
**Progress**: ~80% Complete

## Summary

Refactoring the ExtractorAOIs Windows Service to use BeFirst REST APIs instead of direct SQL queries. This improves maintainability, security, and enables better monitoring and error handling.

